name: Palapa Cafe
address: Jl. Pura Sada No.3, Kapal, Kec. Mengwi, Kabupaten Badung, Bali 80351, Indonesia

We also had the pasta pesto and a rice bowl. Both were perfect. Hope to come back one day.

The interior is cozy but veryyy messy. Sticky table, all furniture in dust.
They don‚Äôt accept international cards

One of Bali traditional dish, made from chicken. Its halal and tasteful.

But, the restaurant doesn't have carpark.
